{"tid":1625239,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"之前中槍中五生打警察手臂係正當防衛","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:43:41.000Z","uid":329551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2695287b7658b433ec038326c9ff9474c403f840","tid":1625239,"uid":329551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60108645?fb_comment_id=2632634573460575_2632715323452500&amp;comment_id=2632715323452500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60108645%3Ffb_comment_id%3D2632634573460575_2632715323452500%26comment_id%3D2632715323452500&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KHd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=b83186b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60108645%3Ffb_comment_id%3D2632634573460575_2632715323452500%26comment_id%3D2632715323452500&h=c43b2a10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60108645?fb_comment_id=2632634573460575_2632715323452500&amp;comment_id=2632715323452500</a><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/asia/100000006745719/hong-kong-protester-shot.html?fbclid=IwAR0MYpwdeoDOHggjCI65slyC2yTbx8GC_t6eFF8fI5pMmTVaplQdiZyBRiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fvideo%2Fworld%2Fasia%2F100000006745719%2Fhong-kong-protester-shot.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0MYpwdeoDOHggjCI65slyC2yTbx8GC_t6eFF8fI5pMmTVaplQdiZyBRiU&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KHd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=bbfc7c2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/asia/100000006745719/hong-kong-protester-shot.html?fbclid=IwAR0MYpwdeoDOHggjCI65slyC2yTbx8GC_t6eFF8fI5pMmTVaplQdiZyBRiU</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n外國傳媒段片見到個警察好冷靜，好似電視上個殺手咁對準佢行埋去，如果個中五生覺得佢會被槍殺，用PVC喉管打警員我覺得係好合嚟嘅正當防衛，唔算單純襲擊。警察全套裝備，警察揸住槍，細佬揸住棍，個細佬應該有合理理由認爲生命受到威脅。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，如果個中五學生枝棍(水喉通)夠力嘅話，佢應該打得甩枝槍。如果枝棍(水喉通)打佢手臂時連佢枝槍都打唔甩，個警員冇合理理由覺得自己會收到嚴重傷害。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得結論係個警察企圖謀殺個中五生，個中五生正當防衛打警員手臂企圖防止被槍殺，力量唔夠最後中彈。<br />\n<br />\n希望有心人能夠聯絡到個中五生，叫佢除咗律師之外唔好同任何人提單案件，因爲當時佢嘅思維同心理狀態好影響辯護策略。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望可以搵到佢個律師將呢啲觀點提出。"},{"pid":"b626dc5d0fcd2be7e9b4fe756417bfe92ced036f","tid":1625239,"uid":313662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"不得不推"},{"pid":"2806bd9f0de7a4728a353f33775bbbe116dbd510","tid":1625239,"uid":215947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjw4n39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpjw4n39.jpg&h=010c6b82&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}